# Walkthrough: Vietnamese Localization & Campaign Alignment

I have localized the "Ad Optimization" feature to Vietnamese and aligned all mock campaigns with US DTC brands (Nike, Sephora, etc.).

## Changes Made

### Documentation
- Updated [PRD](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/docs/PRD.md) and [SRS](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/docs/SRS_01_Chat_Interface.md) to explicitly state that UX writing and AI insights are in Vietnamese.

### Frontend
- **Localizations**:
    - [mockWorkflowData.js](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/frontend/src/data/mockWorkflowData.js): Translated all headers, narratives, comparison labels, and TODO items.
    - [ResultsTable.jsx](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/frontend/src/components/ResultsTable.jsx): Localized table headers and action buttons.
    - [CampaignSelectionTable.jsx](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/frontend/src/components/agent/CampaignSelectionTable.jsx): Localized all UI strings and summary labels.
    - [onboardingData.js](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/frontend/src/data/onboardingData.js): Localized marketing notes and feature descriptions.
- **Brand Alignment**: Updated campaign names to Nike, Sephora US, Best Buy, etc., across all mock data.

### Backend
- **Agent Prompts**: Updated `Narrative Writer` backstory in [agents.py](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/backend/agents.py) to reinforce Vietnamese writing and US brand awareness.
- **Thinking Steps**: Localized the 10-step thinking process generator in [generator.py](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/backend/generator.py) to Vietnamese.

## Verification Results

### Manual Check: Chat Flow
1. **Query**: "Phân tích chiến dịch Nike"
2. **Thinking State**: Displays 10 localized steps (e.g., "Đang truy xuất dữ liệu chiến dịch từ Google Ads API...").
3. **Response Header**: "Đang tối ưu: Nike - Running Shoes Q1".
4. **Narrative**: Fully in Vietnamese, highlighting Nike's performance.
5. **TODO Items**: SMART goals are in Vietnamese (e.g., "Tăng ngân sách chiến dịch...").

### UI Consistency
- Table headers are now "Chiến dịch", "Trạng thái", "Chi phí (30n)", and "ROAS".
- Action buttons are "Xem Traffic Affiliate →" and "Bắt đầu nghiên cứu".

> [!NOTE]
> The mock data generation in [mock_data_generator.py](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/backend/mock_data_generator.py) remains in English for database consistency, but all user-facing strings are now Vietnamese.
